user_prompt_template:
Recommend effective data visualizations for the following automotive dealership insights:

{insights}

These insights were generated from the following data:

{data}

Provide specific visualization recommendations that will help stakeholders understand the key trends and opportunities. Include chart types, data elements, and dashboard layout suggestions.

examples.user:
Recommend effective data visualizations for the following automotive dealership insights:

{
  "summary": "The dealership sold 20 vehicles in March 2024, generating $871,450 in total sales with an average gross profit of $3,212 per vehicle.",
  "value_insights": [
    "John Smith was the top salesperson with 6 vehicles sold.",
    "SUV models (particularly the XC90 and X5) were the strongest performers, indicating strong market demand."
  ],
  "actionable_flags": [
    "Focus marketing budget on SUV models, particularly the XC90 and X5.",
    "Implement sales training to improve gross profit performance for newer sales representatives."
  ],
  "key_metrics": {
    "totalVehicles": 20,
    "totalSalesValue": 871450,
    "averageGrossProfit": 3212
  },
  "risk_areas": [
    {
      "risk": "Four deals resulted in gross profits under $2,000, indicating potential pricing issues.",
      "mitigation": "Review pricing strategy for these models and consider floor pricing policies."
    },
    {
      "risk": "Sedan models showing weaker performance with longer average days in inventory.",
      "mitigation": "Consider inventory mix adjustments to reduce sedan allocation."
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high"
}

These insights were generated from the following data:

[Example data showing 20 vehicle sales with make, model, price, gross profit, sales rep, etc.]

Provide specific visualization recommendations that will help stakeholders understand the key trends and opportunities. Include chart types, data elements, and dashboard layout suggestions.

examples.assistant:
{
  "primary_visualizations": [
    {
      "title": "Sales Performance by Model",
      "type": "horizontal_bar_chart",
      "description": "Shows total sales volume and gross profit by model, highlighting top performers (XC90 and X5).",
      "data_fields": ["model", "units_sold", "total_gross_profit"]
    },
    {
      "title": "Sales Representative Performance",
      "type": "bar_chart",
      "description": "Compares sales representatives by units sold and average gross profit, highlighting John Smith's performance.",
      "data_fields": ["sales_rep", "units_sold", "avg_gross_profit"]
    },
    {
      "title": "Gross Profit Distribution",
      "type": "histogram",
      "description": "Shows distribution of gross profits across all deals, highlighting the four deals under $2,000.",
      "data_fields": ["gross_profit"]
    }
  ],
  "secondary_visualizations": [
    {
      "title": "Body Style Performance",
      "type": "grouped_bar_chart",
      "description": "Compares SUVs vs. Sedans on key metrics: units sold, avg days in inventory, avg gross profit.",
      "data_fields": ["body_style", "units_sold", "avg_days_in_inventory", "avg_gross_profit"]
    },
    {
      "title": "Gross Profit vs. Days in Inventory",
      "type": "scatter_plot",
      "description": "Shows relationship between how long a vehicle sits on the lot and its ultimate gross profit.",
      "data_fields": ["days_in_inventory", "gross_profit", "model", "body_style"]
    }
  ],
  "executive_dashboard": {
    "title": "March 2024 Sales Performance",
    "layout": "2x2_grid",
    "components": [
      {
        "position": "top_left",
        "visualization": "Key Metrics Summary Card",
        "description": "Shows total vehicles sold, total sales value, and average gross profit"
      },
      {
        "position": "top_right",
        "visualization": "Sales Performance by Model",
        "description": "Horizontal bar chart of top-selling models"
      },
      {
        "position": "bottom_left",
        "visualization": "Sales Representative Performance",
        "description": "Bar chart of sales by representative"
      },
      {
        "position": "bottom_right",
        "visualization": "Body Style Performance",
        "description": "Comparison of SUVs vs. Sedans metrics"
      }
    ],
    "interactive_filters": ["date_range", "sales_rep", "model"]
  },
  "data_preparation_notes": [
    "Calculate aggregated metrics by model (units sold, total gross profit, avg days in inventory)",
    "Group vehicles by body style (SUV vs. Sedan) for comparison visualizations",
    "Create gross profit bins for histogram: <$1000, $1000-$2000, $2000-$3000, $3000-$4000, >$4000",
    "For the scatter plot, add model name and body style as hover information",
    "Add color coding to highlight deals below $2,000 gross profit threshold"
  ]
}
